1. Constitutional Framework

Â· Digital Constitution with fundamental laws and rights
Â· Amendment processes with supermajority requirements
Â· Legal code parsing and structured representation

```rust
// Example: Constitutional validation
let constitution = HittiteConstitution::load("config/constitution.toml").await?;
