ğŸ”§ Configuration

Constitutional Configuration

```toml
[constitution]
name = "Digital Hittite Constitution"
version = "1.0.0"

[founding_principles]
rule_of_law = true
representative_government = true
technological_sovereignty = true

[fundamental_rights]
digital_privacy = { level = "high", enforcement = "strict" }
algorithmic_fairness = { level = "high", enforcement = "strict" }

[amendment_process]
proposal_threshold = 0.05
approval_threshold = 0.67
ratification_period = 30
```

Treaty Protocol Configuration

```yaml
treaty_protocol:
  negotiation:
    max_rounds: 10
    timeout_duration: 30d
    mediation_trigger: 0.33
    
  dispute_resolution:
    mechanisms:
      - "automated_mediation"
      - "expert_arbitration" 
      - "constitutional_court"
    enforcement_mechanism: "smart_sanctions"
```

